Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀… 好熱好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太熱了——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中君 從剛才開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就光在說好熱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就已經夠熱的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不停的說熱的話會變得更熱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止說「好熱」！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀… 好夏天好夏天…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱… 真的好夏天吶…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼噠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過可真的是好夏天！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太夏天了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好夏天！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好夏天好夏天…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能揍他了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 好夏天…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好夏天吶！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好夏天！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINY~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不管什麼看起來都是這麼的耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣也是 人們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 就連這教室都是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 我終於做作業了啦——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給美緒看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,……啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧咧咧咧咧咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咧… 咧… 咧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木——有！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是那樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易 難得做一次作業的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥為啥為啥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥木有了啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 看一下別人的不就行了嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美～緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下哦 等下哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卷子——！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉——呦——喂——呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大早上的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人的大侵略…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 又忘記了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少瞧不起我啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是做完了忘記帶來了！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 才沒有瞧不起你吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業是語文卷子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是夾在哪裡了哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細找找看？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剛剛還找了好幾遍呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對… 已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MY GOD！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大福展覽會是個神馬玩意——！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展覽會是個… 什麼玩意喲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上講桌那找一下 說不定會有卷子喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧不是吧！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡——！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惡——！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去取麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也得——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去取！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 要上課了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到座位上去
