Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 立花美里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是因為出了新商品 在猶豫要買哪一個而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 這邊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能聽你說的呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商品 很難喝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以選旁邊的商品比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是因為你推薦才買的呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\shad0\c&H524754&\3c&HCDCCD7&\frz30\pos(294,234)}射擊
