Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord2\c&H5877C3&\3c&HE2D1B6&\frz30\pos(967,230)}炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近搭了幾個攤子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以去看了看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說目標都是射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在電視上看過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天非常期待！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此 才帶了500元啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 一次500萬元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LUCKY 正好500元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也想吃炒麵…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但畢竟今天是為了這個來的吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有奶糖和茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這些麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有是什麼話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這放的可都是名牌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 僅有的一點錢也已經交出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能帶那東西回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上來就瞄著貴的東西可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個可不容易被打下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要先瞄準要掉下來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下來的什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的不只有奶糖這一個選擇了麼
