Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\shad0\bord0\c&H123774&\pos(795,623)}大\N工\N謹\N制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\shad0\bord0\c&H123774&\pos(795,623)\c&H9595AE&}大\N工\N謹\N制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:17.57,STAFF,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\bord0\shad3\c&HDFF7FA&\4c&H2F3A56&\pos(633,555)}奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:18.73,STAFF,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\bord0\shad3\c&HDFF7FA&\pos(633,555)\4c&HD3D4DD&}奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來 奶糖也完全黏在上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再有幾毫米就掉下來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 你技術很不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 是現役職業槍手麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑噠！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這茄子紋絲不動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副無精打采的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是覺得我們耍花招了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們雖然店舖破破爛爛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神飽滿和不耍花招可是素有評定的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對 這絕對是有什麼貓膩啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 那個那個 快看快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釘子 能看見釘子哦 釘子！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是騙人的麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 為什麼什麼話都不說了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這樣是不可以的吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你不還精神滿滿的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼看來奶糖也動了手腳了吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝什麼睡啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩一發了我該瞄什麼啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也別來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很帥的東西！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒～～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔了哦～～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NICE CATCH！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！ SUPER BALL！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很帥的東西！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！ 好可惜！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WOW！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！ SWEETS DREAM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒來遊樂園了 好高興吶——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是來對了呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想喝果汁 把錢包給我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在我這裡保管來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 抱歉吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得自己拿著的話會丟的～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧咧咧咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧… 啊咧咧咧咧咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實… 應該是放在這裡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只有小祐的錢包丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 去失物招領處的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會找到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少錢啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4016元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真詳細吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,410)\bord0\shad0\c&H1E2941&}失物招領處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord0\shad0\pos(1085,127)\c&HCFD7E0&}兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想找一個茶色的錢包 裡面放有蛇皮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 幸好在這找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 一時間都不知所措了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在播報一條尋人啟事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位身著牛仔短褲牛仔襯衣帶著牛仔帽的女孩在找媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相關人士請前往走失兒童中心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\shad0\bord0\c&H00020E&\pos(394,482)}墳\N墓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最怕鬼屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來啦——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei\fs45\an7\bord2\shad0\c&HA5B8CB&\3c&H828688&\pos(112,227)}冰\N淇\N淋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei\fs45\an7\bord2\shad0\c&HA5B8CB&\3c&H828688&\pos(26,229)}冰\N淇\N淋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好3個 是帶走吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我這個 這個和這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個 不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可以說出名字麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是櫻井
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎 不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是因為那個是姓才問你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人一直都說我的姓和名聽起來都像姓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問名字是問商品名的那個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 商品名是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我不太明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\bord2\shad0\c&HD1C8D0&\3c&H827275&\frz10.618\pos(802,114)}家庭餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:49.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fnsimhei\b0\bord2\c&HBFB0BF&\3c&H534662&\pos(838,628)}和\N風\N展\N覽\N會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:54.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\bord2\blur6\pos(55,360)}筷\N子\N架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了吃飽了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就等甜點登場了～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那我也來吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好啦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是麻衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐怎麼樣？ 做好了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～快看快看～！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士也試著帶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們就配成對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士今天是名乃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可以叫我博士哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 小名乃～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 已經夠了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 名乃 剛才你叫我博士了是吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 因為你不是已經把發條拿下來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才就是稍微休息一下而已～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是博士名乃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起玩遊戲麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦 玩什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩博士是我 我是博士的交換遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 博士 不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小名乃請把發條裝上！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 因為我是博士 請把我的發條拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:18:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 玩些什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩卡牌麼～？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\shad0\bord0\c&H135BCB&\frz354.811\pos(908,171)}小點心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\shad0\bord0\frz354.811\pos(836,382)\c&HDF8868&}一點{\c&H322CD3&}Q
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 零食真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我非常珍惜的零食！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士是名乃沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但名乃是博士的話就能吃點心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名乃你就是名乃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那既然我變回名乃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去買晚飯的菜了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士我也要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會買零食哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我買鯊魚巧克力和草莓果汁嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不買
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買嘛～～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不買
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了我的飯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs42}鯊魚巧克力和草莓果汁嘛～～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東雲家 今天也很和睦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:03.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,0)\bord4\blur15\pos(800,360)}閒\N時\N遊\N戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\bord0\shad0\pos(947,128)\c&HDEDED7&}大家的街上\N{\c&H5E5C4F&}有大工漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\bord0\shad0\c&H727473&\pos(903,288)}美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始說英文的話就輸了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛才美緒說英語了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說START的話就SAFE哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那說START之前 先把英文說個夠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那麼多英語麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}隻{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸會唰的一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜開眼睛的話心情變得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:27.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\shad2\pos(80,360)\3c&HD3E1E9&\4c&HD2E4ED&}一\N不\N小\N心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊喲 沒有KISS睡美人就醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 主人！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是汽水喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.71,0:23:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會將變得美味的魔法咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融到這些泡泡裡哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.38,0:23:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話的日常是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十三話！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:07.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}朝起きて　歯を磨いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:10.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あっという間　午後10時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:13.97,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日も　たくさん　笑ったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.72,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}たくさん　ときめいたなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:20.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}友達と　バカみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.35,0:22:23.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}騒いでる　時にも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:26.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}チラチラって　目が合う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:29.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}…偶然、だよね。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:32.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初恋なんて言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.82,0:22:35.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キャラじゃないんだもんっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:41.79,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ねえ　あしたも会えるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:44.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}まぶたを　閉じると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:48.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キラキラ　キミだらけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:51.38,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日も　楽しかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:55.80,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あー　恋　してんだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:03.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}うれしいな　うれしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:06.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}はじめまして　こいごころ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:09.98,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あした　まだ　あえるね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:12.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:17.41,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ゆめで　すぐ　あえるね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:23.58,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:07.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}早晨睡醒後 起床刷牙來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:10.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}不知不覺間 已到晚十點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:13.97,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天也遇到 很多歡樂事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}也有非常多 刺激與緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:20.18,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}和閨中密友 像笨蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.35,0:22:23.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}大聲吵又鬧 偶爾會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:26.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}偶爾瞥向你 四目便相接
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:29.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}這也不過是 偶然事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:32.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初戀什麼的難以說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.82,0:22:35.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}因為我不是這樣的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:41.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}吶 我們明天 也會相見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:44.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}將我的雙眼 合上了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:48.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}腦海中只有 亮晶晶的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:51.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天的我也 開心又愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:55.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}啊 陷入戀愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:03.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}真的好開心 真的好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:06.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}第一次見面 我的愛慕心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:09.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}到明天的話 我們又見面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:12.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}現在晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:17.41,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}在夢中很快 我們會見面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:23.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}現在晚安吧


